# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Clinique Saint-Lucas — Tests API
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Utilisation : VS Code (extension REST Client) ou Rider
#
# IMPORTANT : exécuter d'abord la requête "Login" (§ Auth),
# puis copier le token dans la variable @token ci-dessous.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@base = http://localhost:5150

# ── Coller ici le token reçu après le login ─────────────────
@token = COLLER_LE_TOKEN_ICI


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TEST — publics (pas de token nécessaire)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Test de connectivité → 200 + { success: true }
GET {{base}}/test
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Test image → 200 + { imageUrl }
GET {{base}}/test/image
Accept: application/json

###


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUTH — publics
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 3. Login valide → 200 + token JWT  ← EXÉCUTER EN PREMIER
POST {{base}}/api/patients/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@clinique.be",
  "password": "Patient2026!"
}

###

### 4. Login mauvais mot de passe → 401
POST {{base}}/api/patients/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@clinique.be",
  "password": "mauvaisMotDePasse"
}

###

### 5. Login email inconnu → 401
POST {{base}}/api/patients/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "inconnu@test.com",
  "password": "Patient2026!"
}

###

### 6. Register → 501 (non disponible)
POST {{base}}/api/patients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nouveau@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VÉRIFICATION DU BLOCAGE — sans token → 401
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 7. Services sans token → 401
GET {{base}}/api/services
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Team sans token → 401
GET {{base}}/api/team
Accept: application/json

###


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HOMEPAGE — protégé 🔒
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 9. Homepage → 200 + hero, stats, sections
GET {{base}}/api/homepage
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SERVICES — protégés 🔒
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 10. Liste des services → 200 + tableau (6 entrées)
GET {{base}}/api/services
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Service id=1 (Urgences) → 200
GET {{base}}/api/services/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 12. Service id=3 (Pédiatrie) → 200
GET {{base}}/api/services/3
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Service id=99 (inexistant) → 404
GET {{base}}/api/services/99
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DÉPARTEMENTS — protégés 🔒
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 14. Liste des départements → 200 + tableau (4 entrées)
GET {{base}}/api/departments
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 15. Département id=1 (Cardiologie) → 200
GET {{base}}/api/departments/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. Département id=4 (Neurologie) → 200
GET {{base}}/api/departments/4
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 17. Département id=99 (inexistant) → 404
GET {{base}}/api/departments/99
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


