# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FORMULAIRES POST — protégés 🔒
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 26. Contact valide → 200 + referenceId
POST {{base}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "lastName":  "Dupont",
  "email":     "jean.dupont@test.be",
  "subject":   "Demande d'information",
  "message":   "Bonjour, je souhaite des informations sur le service de cardiologie."
}

###

### 27. Contact champs manquants → 400
POST {{base}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "email":     "",
  "message":   ""
}

###

### 28. Rendez-vous valide → 200 + appointmentId
POST {{base}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "firstName":     "Marie",
  "lastName":      "Martin",
  "email":         "marie.martin@test.be",
  "phone":         "+32 477 12 34 56",
  "doctorId":      1,
  "serviceId":     2,
  "preferredDate": "2026-04-15",
  "reason":        "Consultation de suivi cardiologique"
}

###

### 29. Rendez-vous sans email → 400
POST {{base}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "firstName":     "Marie",
  "lastName":      "Martin",
  "email":         "",
  "preferredDate": "2026-04-15"
}

###

### 30. Rendez-vous sans token → 401
POST {{base}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName":     "Marie",
  "lastName":      "Martin",
  "email":         "marie@test.be",
  "preferredDate": "2026-04-15"
}

###
